videos.headline: Jackson's big run puts Louisville on two-yard line
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson's 22-yard run sets them up at the Murray State two-yard line.

videos.headline: Lamar Jackson bursts into end zone for games 1st TD
videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson fakes the handoff and sprints into the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Botched punt puts Louisville just outside the red zone
videos.description: L.J. Gainey fumbles the punt return and it is recovered by Louisville's Lamarques Thomas on the Murray State 21.

videos.headline: Jackson to Fitzpatrick extends Cardinals lead
videos.description: Lamar Jackson finds Dez Fitzpatrick for a 9-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Jackson finds Fitzpatrick again for a TD
videos.description: Lamar Jackson connects with Dez Fitzpatrick for 9 yards in the end zone for the second time today

videos.headline: Jackson's 4th TD pushes Cardinals' lead
videos.description: Lamar Jackson finds Charles Standberry for an 8-yard touchdown.  Jackson's third touchdown pass of the game.

videos.headline: Bonnafon rushes into the end zone for a TD
videos.description: Reggie Bonnafon runs six yards for a Cardinals touchdown right before the half.

videos.headline: Reed botches big play
videos.description: Lamar Jackson finds Corey Reed for a 57-yard pass but Reed fumbles and Murray State recovers it.

videos.headline: Murray State's scoop and score gives them 1st TD of the day
videos.description: Louisville's fumble is scooped up by Jason Johnson and returned 23 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Bagley's TD widens the Cardinals lead
videos.description: Jawon Pass finds Javonte Bagley for the 14-yard touchdown in the third quarter.
